{"tid":1300472,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[拒絕善忘] 提返大家明日大愚一萬億係咩概念","createTime":"2019-07-09T11:22:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T11:44:33.000Z","uid":177089,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"330d121834b52bc05d35a5ef27dec51e24330df1","tid":1300472,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:22:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NtFDAL0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNtFDAL0.png&h=ad90bf28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上圖係2017年全球頭十軍費開支表<br />\n單位係十億美金 <br />\n<br />\n換算返之後 明日大愚開支大約1300億美元（下同）<br />\n<br />\n全頭頭三位（不計算歐盟）<br />\n美國一年軍費開支係6100億<br />\n支那係2280億<br />\n阿拉伯係695億<br />\n<br />\n但你唔好唔記得 香港只係一個彈丸城市<br />\n1000幾頃土地 而以上幾個大國 <br />\n係世上無論人口同土地都可以稱為列強<br />\n如果香港用呢筆錢去建軍會點？<br />\n<br />\n再睇下亞洲最強之一嘅新加坡<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RU0zTzz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRU0zTzz.png&h=1aa5e9c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n只係102億<br />\n<br />\n即係話大愚個舊錢 如果用嚟建立一支軍隊<br />\n已經係一支高度科技化嘅部隊 就算唔額外注資<br />\n都可以運作接近十年！！<br />\n<br />\n你可能話香港人又瘦又弱又廢<br />\n邊會肯當兵 邊會捱到<br />\n我同你講 收皮喇你<br />\n根本無野係錢解決唔到<br />\n有一舊咁撚大嘅錢<br />\n真係要訓練嘅 請啲外國軍官嚟教 <br />\n阿源都可以練到變特種部隊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記住點解當初中共唔要包攬你國防同唔俾香港人當兵<br />\n係因為驚你反抗 <br />\n如果以香港人嘅智力同財力 再加上對香港嘅歸屬感<br />\n香港根本有能力反攻大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同台灣一齊消滅支共"},{"pid":"f5e1a79fbfe478e1c20a7964a858a63125746181","tid":1300472,"uid":137459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:23:02.000Z","msg":"《一日爭取唔到真普選，我地永遠處於被動》<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1299151\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1299151</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3540580507d382dd0d7a954418b1059e3b2ab6e2","tid":1300472,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:23:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1d47537c65c46a5725771176c6990e615e1093d","tid":1300472,"uid":120705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:23:54.000Z","msg":"明日大愚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c50bb7d6a02cbd88b002b60d8792e1fb6bcd9376","tid":1300472,"uid":24400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:25:37.000Z","msg":"港獨是唯一出路"},{"pid":"2363949570681c0d849898b114f6d7c008a08c6c","tid":1300472,"uid":23189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:32:52.000Z","msg":"歡迎入內討論<br />\n<br />\n「長文慎入」勇武又好、和理非又好，自己香港自己救！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1299934/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1299934/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"68515f51b790fc7aee6b6f68a7e4c3c6a9b359cb","tid":1300472,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:37:34.000Z","msg":"記住中共最驚嘅唔係失去香港 <br />\n係失勢<br />\n<br />\n佢驚香港輸出革命 驚香港有推倒佢嘅能力"},{"pid":"3e2a88aa561bff6dd6cd3e7ccf7d65d4d563fe3d","tid":1300472,"uid":886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:38:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3af49c81fe6347bf136c976c62697207abbcd694","tid":1300472,"uid":267395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:44:33.000Z","msg":"屌你它母支那族 攬炒都唔撚比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}